'''Kinegamori Kofun''' ({{ill|Kinegamori Kofun|ja|杵ガ森古墳|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinegamori Kofun|qq=}}) is a [[:en:Zenpokoenfun|Zenpokoenfun]] located in [[:en:Aizubange|Aizubange]], [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]]. It is part of the {{ill|Unai Aotsu Kofun Group|ja|宇内青津古墳群|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Unai Aotsu Kofun Group|qq=}} and is Historic Site1 as a Fukushima Prefecture Historic Site.

Kinegamori Kofun is recognized as one of the oldest kofun in the Tohoku region.

